data.description: This home has it all! 3 levels, in ground pool, 2 car carport, 1 car garage, detached 2 car garage with upstairs that could be finished for rental income potential or in law suite! Yes! Five covered parking locations!! Semi open floor plan. Fenced in back yard. Pool fenced separately. Jacuzzi tub. Walk in closets. Quiet neighborhood. All this and only a 30 minute drive to Huntsville!! Free appraisal and $1400 toward closing costs if you use our preferred lender.
